2
00:00:23,641 --> 00:00:24,725
D'oh!

3
00:00:24,884 --> 00:00:26,051
(tires screeching)

4
00:00:26,298 --> 00:00:27,371
(grunts)

5
00:00:27,453 --> 00:00:29,652
